ames Keenan) <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tool-frontman-maynard-james-keenan-earns-black-belt-in-brazilian-jiu-jitsu-3570339">获得了巴西柔术黑带</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-tool-play-flood-for-the-first-time-in-13-years-3570482">Watch Tool 后剧《Flood》13 年来首次</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次亮相。</p> ;
